title.en: Unmei no Tsugai? Naraba Sono Akai Ito Toyara Kirisutete Sashiagemashou
Reiketsu Ryuuou Heika no "Unmei no Tsugai" rashii Desu ga, Koukyuu ni Hikikomorou to Omoimasu
Ochibure Saijo no Koufuku Heika ni Suterareta no de, Saiai no Hito wo Sukui ni ikimasu
Konyaku Haki Shita Aite ga Mainichi Shazai ni Kimasu ga, Fukuen Nante Zettai ni Ariemasen!
Suterareta Jimi Oujo wa Byakurou Denka ni Dekiaisareru
Migawari Konyaku Shananoni, Gin Ookami Heika ga Doushitemo Hanashite Kuremasen!
Watashi no Konyakusha-sama no Dokuzetsu ga Sugiru ~Minna ni Shio Taiou no Hazu ga Watashi wa Dekiai Sareteimasu~
Honmono no Seijo Janai to Bareta no ni, Outei Denka ni Semararete imasu
Irazu no Hime wa Jinrou no Kuni de Aisare Ouhi to naru!
Eiyuu-sama, Wakeari Osanazuma wa Ikagan desu ka?
Seijo no Ane desu ga, Naze ka Miwaku no Koushaku-sama ni Tsukaeru Koto ni narimashita
Toraware Hanahime no Shiawase na Gosan
Kon'yakusha ga Uwaki Aite to Kakeochi shimashita. Ouji Denka ni Dekiaisarete Shiawase na no de, Imasara Modoritai to Iwarete mo Komarimasu.
Gimai ga Seijo dakara to Konyakuhaki Saremashita ga, Watashi wa Yousei no Itoshigo desu
Ochikobore Reijou wa, Koushaku Kakka kara no Dekiai ni Kizukanai ~Konyakusha ni Shimeisareta no wa Saishoku Kenbi no Ane de wa Naku, Watashi deshita~
Kono Ai wa, Kokuou Heika no Gomeirei Janai - Ohitori-sama Kibou no Reijou desu ga, Funaka na Kishi ga Hanashitekuremasen!
